  "text": "Rendering the image requires a high level of accuracy, which is provided by real-time computer graphics techniques. Physically-based shaders simulates materials and light based on measured physical parameters [CITATION_1] . Coupled with faster hardware, the images render within a few milliseconds [CITATION_2] .",
